If you have any problems, please contact us at support@baseussecurity.com. 

Baseus security offers the most comprehensive voice-controlled smart home experience. Control your security devices hands-free. Just say it, Baseus security will obey. 
Here’s a step by step guide: 
(1) Download our "baseus Security" app in Google Play or iOS App Store; 
(2) Launch the app and register a new account (or login if you’re already registered); 
(3) Turn on Baseus security devices and connect them with “baseus Security” app; 
(4) Download Amazon "Alexa" app from Amazon Market, Google Play or iOS App Store, and 
connect Echo with "Alexa" app; 
(5) Search the Alexa Skills directory for "Baseus Security Camera"; 
(6) Click Enable skill of "Baseus Security Camera", you'll be navigated to the login page, follow the instructions on the page to complete linking; 
(7) Talk to Echo "Alexa,discover devices". Wait till Echo says "Discover is completed"; 
(8) Now all setup is done. Try talk to Echo to control your devices:
Alexa, show me the camera.
Alexa, show me the backyard camera.
